    <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         Widget Text Position Offsets
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         These dimensions control the position of text elements within
         the home screen widgets. Themes can override these values to
         reposition text to match their layout design.

         Positive values shift the element in the direction of the
         named axis (e.g. offset_top="4dp" moves text 4dp down).
         Negative values shift in the opposite direction.

         All values are in dp (density-independent pixels).
         Remove or set to 0dp for default positioning.
         ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

